      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-tes-reg-100
                     vis-tes-reg-200
                     vis-tes-reg-300
                     vis-tes-reg-400
                     vis-tes-reg-500
                     vis-tes-reg-600
                     depending            on   w-cnt-sts-imp-npt      .
           go to     vis-tes-reg-999.
       vis-tes-reg-100.
