           go to     vis-tes-reg-999.
       vis-tes-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts testata                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-tes-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase linee impegnate dalla testata a seconda   *
      *              * del numero pagina                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-npt    =    1
                     move 07              to   v-lin
           else      move 04              to   v-lin                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione del numero pagina        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-tes-reg-100
                     pmt-tes-reg-200
                     pmt-tes-reg-300
                     pmt-tes-reg-400
                     pmt-tes-reg-500
                     pmt-tes-reg-600
                     depending            on   w-cnt-sts-imp-npt      .
           go to     pmt-tes-reg-999.
       pmt-tes-reg-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice archivio                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-cod-arc-000      thru pmt-cod-arc-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice dipendenza cliente                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-dpz-cli-000      thru pmt-dpz-cli-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo indirizzo di spedizione                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tip-ids-000      thru pmt-tip-ids-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo fornitura                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tip-frn-000      thru pmt-tip-frn-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Si/no ordine da verificare                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-snx-oav-000      thru pmt-snx-oav-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-tes-reg-999.
       pmt-tes-reg-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice archivio per fatturazione                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-arc-plf-000      thru pmt-arc-plf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenza archivio per fatturazione            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-dpz-plf-000      thru pmt-dpz-plf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
