      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-snx-sps-000      thru pmt-snx-sps-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice primo vettore                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-cod-vet-000      thru pmt-cod-vet-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
