      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-com-int-000      thru pmt-com-int-999        .
           go to     pmt-tes-reg-999.
       pmt-tes-reg-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Inoltro documenti                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
