      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice nostro c/c postale per pagamento         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-nos-ccp-000      thru pmt-nos-ccp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo addebito spese incasso                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-add-spi-000      thru pmt-add-spi-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Si/No addebito spese bollo                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-add-spb-000      thru pmt-add-spb-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Data scadenza manuale pagamento                 *
